text: Gokavaram Mandal is one of the 64 mandals in East Godavari District of Andhra Pradesh. As per census 2011, there are 14 villages. == Demographics == Gokavaram Mandal has total population of 69,596 as per the Census 2011 out of which 34,352 are males while 35,244 are females and the average Sex Ratio of Gokavaram Mandal is 1,026. The total literacy rate of Gokavaram Mandal is 62.92%.
